commit bc91d337d7cf765fd23e47783a498e4b3b334f39
Author: Peter Hutterer <peter.hutterer@who-t.net>
Date:   Thu Oct 20 08:42:53 2016 +1000

    Fix potential NULL pointer dereferencing
    
