Date:   Thu Oct 20 08:27:01 2016 +1000

    Remove two unused variables
    
    They were never used anyway
    
    Signed-off-by: Peter Hutterer <peter.hutterer@who-t.net>

commit bf7fffde520277e13b350950de9dc5bf89858951
