Date:   Wed Oct 19 11:42:57 2016 +1000

    Don't init the horiz scroll property on non-pointer devices
    
    Signed-off-by: Peter Hutterer <peter.hutterer@who-t.net>

commit 728217775626e2086d7c3acd0d242562390f145b
