Date:   Thu Jan 28 15:02:54 2016 +1000

    Fix compiler warnings about missing tablet event cases
    
    Signed-off-by: Peter Hutterer <peter.hutterer@who-t.net>

commit e8f5394b0734db41abd15ab72457aea99c25d9ab
