Date:   Fri Nov 13 10:48:02 2015 +1000

    Don't fail DEVICE_CLOSE
    
    We're not doing anything here, so no reason to fail.
    
    Signed-off-by: Peter Hutterer <peter.hutterer@who-t.net>

