    Initialize variable 'path' to NULL to silence warning
    
      CC       libinput.lo
    libinput.c: In function 'xf86libinput_pre_init':
    libinput.c:1222:2: warning: 'path' may be used uninitialized in this
    function [-Wmaybe-uninitialized]
      free(path);
